WEBVTT

00:00:59.064 --> 00:01:01.037
He is introduced to this young woman.

00:01:01.037 --> 00:01:02.752
He eventually gets married.

00:01:02.752 --> 00:01:05.557
He starts this new life.

00:01:05.557 --> 00:01:08.483
He has a purpose in life.

00:01:08.483 --> 00:01:11.257
One beautiful day in Mogadishu,

00:01:11.257 --> 00:01:14.145
under an azure blue sky,

00:01:14.145 --> 00:01:16.666
a car bomb goes off.

00:01:16.666 --> 00:01:19.861
That small town kid with the big city dreams

00:01:19.861 --> 00:01:22.109
was the suicide bomber,

00:01:22.109 --> 00:01:24.467
and that dynamic group of people

00:01:24.467 --> 00:01:26.836
were al Shabaab, a terrorist organization

00:01:26.836 --> 00:01:30.517
linked to al Qaeda.